msgctxt "72_GG"
msgid "[This... can't... be...!]"
msgstr "[¡Esto... no... puede ser...!]"

msgctxt "84_Nair"
msgid "[Give up! It's over for you!]"
msgstr "[¡Ríndete! ¡Se acabó para ti!]"

msgctxt "96_GG"
msgid "[All I ever wanted was for you－just you－to be happy, Nair...]"
msgstr "[Todo lo que siempre quise fue que tú - solo tú - fueras feliz,\n"
"Nair...]"

msgctxt "108_Nair"
msgid "[If that's the way you truly feel, then pay for your sins with the rest of your life.]"
msgstr "[Si de verdad te sientes así, entonces paga. Paga por tus\n"
"pecados por el resto de tu vida.]"

msgctxt "120_Nair"
msgid "[That's my final wish, as your only family...]"
msgstr "[Ese es mi último deseo, como la única familia que te queda...]"

msgctxt "132_GG"
msgid "[......]"
msgstr "[......]"

msgctxt "144_Tanimura"
msgid "[Why did you kill your parents for money? You're the eldest son. You would have inherited the money either way, right?]"
msgstr "[¿Por qué mataste tus padres? Eres el hijo mayor. Habrías\n"
"heredado todo ese dinero de todas formas. ¿Por qué?]"

msgctxt "156_GG"
msgid "[Those brainless idiots were wasting their own inheritance. How could I expect to inherit anything of my own? Waiting would've been futile.]"
msgstr "[Esos idiotas solo malgastaban el dinero. ¿Cómo podría esperar\n"
"a heredar algo? Esperar solo habría sido inútil.]"

msgctxt "168_GG"
msgid "[I tried reasoning with them. I even majored in management at college, but they would never even acknowledge what I was saying.]"
msgstr "[Trate de razonar con ellos, incluso en la universidad me\n"
"especialice en administración. Pero ellos nunca tomaron\n"
"en cuenta ni una sola palabra de lo que les decía.]"

msgctxt "180_GG"
msgid "[They were so incompetent, they didn't even have the faculties to take notice of my talent.]"
msgstr "[Eran unos incompetentes, ni siquiera tuvieron las facultades\n"
"de reconocer mi talento.]"

msgctxt "192_GG"
msgid "[What's more, they didn't trust me, and were even looking for a new successor.]"
msgstr "[Incluso, ni siquiera confiaban en mí. Estaban en busca de un\n"
"nuevo sucesor.]"

msgctxt "204_GG"
msgid "[They had no intention whatsoever to leave the family fortune to me and Nair.]"
msgstr "[Ellos no tenían ninguna intención de dejarnos la fortuna\n"
"familiar a Nair y a mí.]"

msgctxt "216_Nair"
msgid "[It is true that our parents weren't interested in anything but money.]"
msgstr "[Eso es cierto. Nuestros padres solo estaban interesados por\n"
"el dinero.]"

msgctxt "228_Nair"
msgid "[But you made the wrong decision. Nobody has the right to kill another.]"
msgstr "[Pero tú tomaste la decisión equivocada. Nadie tiene derecho\n"
"a quitarle la vida a otra persona.]"

msgctxt "240_GG"
msgid "[......]"
msgstr "[......]"

msgctxt "252_GG"
msgid "[Nair, you've grown up to be a wonderful person. I can rest easy knowing that.]"
msgstr "[Nair, te has convertido en una persona maravillosa. Puedo\n"
"descansar tranquilo sabiéndolo.]"

msgctxt "264_Nair"
msgid "[......]"
msgstr "[......]"

msgctxt "276_Nair"
msgid "[Tanimura-san...]"
msgstr "[Tanimura-san...]"

msgctxt "288_Tanimura"
msgid "[I know, Nair. I know.]"
msgstr "[Lo sé, Nair... Lo sé.]"

msgctxt "312_Tanimura"
msgid "This is Tanimura from the Community Safety Division. I need men on the roof of the Millennium Tower right away."
msgstr "Soy Tanimura de la División de Seguridad Comunitaria. Necesito\n"
"que envíen hombres en la azotea de la Torre Millennium, de\n"
"inmediato."

msgctxt "396_Nair"
msgid "[Tanimura-san, thanks for everything. You really helped me a lot.]"
msgstr "[Tanimura-san, gracias por todo. Me ayudaste mucho con todo\n"
"esto.]"

msgctxt "408_Tanimura"
msgid "[I guess you were pretty shocked to find out the murderer was really your brother.]"
msgstr "[Debes estar muy sorprendida al descubrir que el asesino era\n"
"en realidad tu hermano.]"

msgctxt "420_Nair"
msgid "[Well, of course. But honestly, I'm a little happy to see that he's still alive.]"
msgstr "[Bueno, sí lo estoy. Pero honestamente, estoy un poco feliz de\n"
"saber que todavía sigue con vida.]"

msgctxt "432_Tanimura"
msgid "[Really?]"
msgstr "[¿De verdad?]"

msgctxt "444_Nair"
msgid "[Well, we got the bad guy. But I bet I'm going to be pretty busy for a while after this.]"
msgstr "[Bueno, atrapamos al criminal. Pero apuesto a que voy a estar\n"
"muy ocupada por un largo tiempo después de esto.]"

msgctxt "456_Tanimura"
msgid "[Why's that?]"
msgstr "[¿Y eso, por qué?]"

msgctxt "468_Nair"
msgid "[For starters, GG is going to be interrogated here in Japan, right? I also have to start on the extradition paperwork.]"
msgstr "[Para empezar, el interrogatorio de GG será aquí en Japón, ¿no?\n"
"Además, tengo que empezar con el papeleo de extradición.]"

msgctxt "480_Tanimura"
msgid "[Oh, I see. So the worst of all of this is yet to come.]"
msgstr "[Ah, entiendo. Así que lo peor aún está por venir.]"

msgctxt "492_Nair"
msgid "[Tanimura-san! You're not going to help?]"
msgstr "[¿Eh? ¡Tanimura-san! ¿No vas a ayudarme?]"

msgctxt "504_Tanimura"
msgid "[I think I'll pass on that part. I wish you all the best, Nair.]"
msgstr "[Creo que esa parte me la saltaré. Te deseo lo mejor Nair.]"

msgctxt "516_Nair"
msgid "[Hey! You can't leave me now!]"
msgstr "[¡Oye! ¡No puedes abandonarme ahora!]"

msgctxt "528_Nair"
msgid "[...Just kidding!]"
msgstr "[Je..., solo bromeo.]"

msgctxt "540_Nair"
msgid "[You were more help than I could have ever imagined. We'll take care of the rest.]"
msgstr "[Fuiste de mucha más ayuda de lo que me hubiera imaginado. Nos\n"
"ocuparemos del resto.]"

msgctxt "552_Nair"
msgid "[There has to be some way I can repay you.]"
msgstr "[Tiene que haber alguna manera en la que pueda compensarte.]"

msgctxt "564_Tanimura"
msgid "[No worries. I was just doing my job.]"
msgstr "[No te preocupes. Solo hacia mi trabajo.]"

msgctxt "576_Tanimura"
msgid "[Plus, you taught me lots of new techniques. The whole experience was pretty inspirational too. That's enough reward for me.]"
msgstr "[Además, me enseñaste muchas técnicas nuevas. Todo esto fue\n"
"bastante inspirador. Eso es suficiente para mí.]"

msgctxt "600_Nair"
msgid "[You're too nice.]"
msgstr "[Eres demasiado amable.]"

msgctxt "612_Nair"
msgid "[When I get back home I'll send you a bunch of fresh fruit!]"
msgstr "[¡Cuando regrese a casa, te enviaré un montón de fruta fresca!]"

msgctxt "624_Tanimura"
msgid "[Well, I am partial to fruit. I'll be looking forward to it then.]"
msgstr "[Bueno, me encanta la fruta. Estaré esperándolas.]"

msgctxt "636_Marcos"
msgid "[Nair! Come here and help me fill these forms out!]"
msgstr "[¡Nair! ¡Ven aquí y ayúdame a rellenar estos formularios!]"

msgctxt "648_Nair"
msgid "[Be right there!]"
msgstr "[¡Ya voy!]"

msgctxt "660_Nair"
msgid "[Well, this is it, Tanimura-san. Thanks again.]"
msgstr "[Bien, esto fue todo, Tanimura-san. Gracias otra vez.]"

msgctxt "672_Tanimura"
msgid "[Right back at ya.]"
msgstr "[Lo mismo digo.]"

msgctxt "684_Nair"
msgid "[See you around!]"
msgstr "[¡Nos vemos luego!]"

msgctxt "756_Nair"
msgid "[Marcos! Garcia!]"
msgstr "[¡Marcos! ¡Garcia!]"

msgctxt "768_Tanimura"
msgid "[Wait. Isn't that...]"
msgstr "[Espera. Ese es...]"

msgctxt "792_Nair"
msgid "[GG.]"
msgstr "[GG.]"

msgctxt "804_GG"
msgid "[I must give you credit for making it this far. However, your coming here was a mistake.]"
msgstr "[Debo darte el mérito por haber llegado tan lejos. Sin embargo,\n"
"venir hasta aquí fue un error.]"

msgctxt "816_GG"
msgid "[And I take it you realize that now, no?]"
msgstr "[Supongo que ahora te das cuenta de eso, ¿no?]"

msgctxt "840_Nair"
msgid "[It can't be!]"
msgstr "[¡No puede ser!]"

msgctxt "852_Tanimura"
msgid "[Are you sure that's GG?]"
msgstr "[¿Estás segura de que este es GG?]"

msgctxt "864_Nair"
msgid "[Yeah...]"
msgstr "[Sí...]"

msgctxt "876_Tanimura"
msgid "[Nair! What's gotten into you!?]"
msgstr "[¡Nair! ¿Qué te pasa?]"

msgctxt "888_GG"
msgid "[Can't blame you for being surprised. This is why I told you coming would be a mistake.]"
msgstr "[No te culpo por sentirte sorprendida. Por eso te dije que venir\n"
"sería un error.]"

msgctxt "900_Tanimura"
msgid "[What's going on?]"
msgstr "[¿Qué está pasando?]"

msgctxt "912_Nair"
msgid "[......]"
msgstr "[......]"

msgctxt "924_Nair"
msgid "[He's... my brother...]"
msgstr "[Él es... mi hermano...]"

msgctxt "936_Tanimura"
msgid "[Your what!?]"
msgstr "[¡¿Tú qué?!]"

msgctxt "948_Nair"
msgid "[But why...?]"
msgstr "[Pero... ¿Por qué?]"

msgctxt "960_GG"
msgid "[It's just as it appears. I killed our parents, faked my death, and took off with our family's massive fortune.]"
msgstr "[Es tal y como parece. Yo mate a nuestros padres, fingí mi\n"
"muerte y me hice con la millonaria fortuna de nuestra familia.]"

msgctxt "972_Nair"
msgid "[It can't be...]"
msgstr "[No puede ser...]"

msgctxt "984_GG"
msgid "[I'm afraid it can. But the facts reported on the murder are all lies.]"
msgstr "[Me temo que sí. Pero los hechos reportados del asesinato son\n"
"puras mentiras.]"

msgctxt "996_Tanimura"
msgid "[What do you mean?]"
msgstr "[¿Mentiras?]"

msgctxt "1008_GG"
msgid "[Our family operated a plant, dealing mainly with automobile manufacturing.]"
msgstr "[Nuestra familia dirigía una fábrica, que se dedicaba\n"
"principalmente a la fabricación de automóviles.]"

msgctxt "1020_GG"
msgid "[But that business alone could never amass such wealth.]"
msgstr "[Pero ese negocio por sí solo nunca podría acumular tanta\n"
"riqueza.]"

msgctxt "1032_GG"
msgid "[It was merely a front. Behind the scenes, they dealt in the munitions industry－selling arms. This was the true source of their enormous wealth.]"
msgstr "[No era más que una fachada. La realidad es que detrás de eso,\n"
"se dedicaban a la industria armamentística - vendiendo armas.\n"
"Esa era su verdadera fuente de ingresos y riqueza.]"

msgctxt "1044_GG"
msgid "[Wealth that I took.]"
msgstr "[La riqueza con la cual me apropie.]"

msgctxt "1056_GG"
msgid "[Publicizing my death freed me from all political and economic responsibility. Living behind the scenes has many advantages.]"
msgstr "[Divulgar mi muerte me libero de toda responsabilidad política y\n"
"económica. Vivir sin ser el foco de atención tiene muchas\n"
"ventajas.]"

msgctxt "1068_Nair"
msgid "[It can't be...]"
msgstr "[No puede ser...]"

msgctxt "1080_Tanimura"
msgid "[Nobody can just fake their death that easily!]"
msgstr "[¡Nadie puede fingir su muerte así de fácil!]"

msgctxt "1092_GG"
msgid "[Perhaps not in Japan. But the sleuthing techniques aren't so advanced where I'm from. It was hardly a challenge to find a loophole.]"
msgstr "[Quizás no en Japón. Pero las técnicas de investigación no son\n"
"tan desarrolladas en mi país. No fue difícil encontrar un vacío\n"
"legal.]"

msgctxt "1104_GG"
msgid "[And I'm rich. Nothing is impossible for me now.]"
msgstr "[Además, soy millonario. Nada es imposible para mí ahora.]"

msgctxt "1116_Tanimura"
msgid "[This guy's ridiculous.]"
msgstr "[Este tipo es ridículo.]"

msgctxt "1128_GG"
msgid "[My parents and I never saw eye-to-eye when it came to their money. I had to get rid of them.]"
msgstr "[Mis padres y yo nunca coincidimos cuando se trataba de dinero.\n"
"Tuve que deshacerme de ellos.]"

msgctxt "1140_GG"
msgid "[But Nair and Marcos were always there for me when I was alone.]"
msgstr "[Pero Nair y Marcos siempre estuvieron para mí cuando yo estaba solo.]"

msgctxt "1152_GG"
msgid "[I am grateful to both of them.]"
msgstr "[Les estoy muy agradecido a ambos.]"

msgctxt "1164_Tanimura"
msgid "[That's why you told them to stay out of your way, right? You didn't want to kill them.]"
msgstr "[Fue por eso que les dijiste que no se metieran, ¿verdad?\n"
"No querías matarlos.]"

msgctxt "1176_GG"
msgid "[That's right.]"
msgstr "[Así es.]"

msgctxt "1188_Tanimura"
msgid "[Even wicked people like you aren't able to forget the people they love.]"
msgstr "[Incluso personas despreciables como tú, no son capaces de\n"
"olvidar a las personas que aman.]"

msgctxt "1200_Tanimura"
msgid "[But do you think your friend and sister are happy with you now?]"
msgstr "[¿Pero crees que tu hermana y tu amigo están felices por ti\n"
"ahora?]"

msgctxt "1212_GG"
msgid "[That's why I told them not to interfere. If they figured out who I really was, I would have to dispose of them regardless.]"
msgstr "[Por eso les dije que no se metieran en mis asuntos.\n"
"Sí, descubrían mi identidad, tendría que eliminarlos.]"

msgctxt "1224_Nair"
msgid "[Dispose?]"
msgstr "[¿Eliminarlos?]"

msgctxt "1236_Tanimura"
msgid "[You gave yourself away the moment you said that word.]"
msgstr "[Te delataste en el momento que dijiste esas palabras.]"

msgctxt "1248_Tanimura"
msgid "[If these people were truly important to you, you'd never talk of \"disposing\" them. Not ever.]"
msgstr "[Si esas personas de verdad fueran importantes para ti, nunca\n"
"dirías algo como \"eliminarlos\" nunca jamás.]"

msgctxt "1260_Tanimura"
msgid "[I'm sure even Nair has realized the truth about you now.]"
msgstr "[Estoy seguro de que incluso Nair se ha dado cuenta de quién\n"
"eres en realidad.]"

msgctxt "1272_GG"
msgid "[......]"
msgstr "[......]"

msgctxt "1284_Nair"
msgid "[......]"
msgstr "[......]"

msgctxt "1296_Nair"
msgid "[You're not my brother. My brother is nothing like you.]"
msgstr "[Tú no eres mi hermano. Él no se parece en nada a ti.]"

msgctxt "1308_Nair"
msgid "[My brother is dead! My brother died that day, along with my parents!]"
msgstr "[¡Mi hermano está muerto! ¡Él murió ese día!\n"
"Murió, junto a mis padres.]"

msgctxt "1320_GG"
msgid "[......]"
msgstr "[......]"

msgctxt "1332_Nair"
msgid "[You're just the criminal that murdered my family now. And you're not getting away with it.]"
msgstr "[Eres el criminal que asesino a mi familia. Y no te vas a salir\n"
"con la tuya.]"

msgctxt "1344_GG"
msgid "[That's too bad. I would have thought you of all people would at least try to understand.]"
msgstr "[Que lastima. Pensaba que tú, de entre todas las personas,\n"
"podría llegar a entenderlo.]"

msgctxt "1356_Tanimura"
msgid "[You can't force your ideas onto other people and expect them to agree with you.]"
msgstr "[No puedes imponer tus propósitos y esperar que las personas\n"
"estén de acuerdo contigo.]"

msgctxt "1368_GG"
msgid "[That's enough. You will die now.]"
msgstr "[Ya fue suficiente. Ahora van a morir.]"

msgctxt "1380_Nair"
msgid "[I'm going to make you pay. Count on it.]"
msgstr "[Te voy a hacer pagar. Tenlo por seguro.]"

msgctxt "1392_GG"
msgid "[I grow tired of this banter. Prepare yourself!]"
msgstr "[Ya me cansé de bromas. ¡Prepárate!]"

